From: BeneSys Fix <fix@benesys.in>
Date: Thu, 19 Mar 2026 13:04:33 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] fix: Tab key completely blocked from sidebar - all nav links
 get tabIndex=-1

- Added tabIndex={-1} to ALL sidebar Link elements (9 links)
- Added tabIndex={-1} to Logout button
- Navigation hook skips any element with tabIndex=-1
- Navigation hook skips anything inside aside/nav/[data-slot=sidebar]
- Tab/Enter now stays strictly within form fields only
